{{Expand Serbian|Светозар Кољевић|date=April 2014}} '''Svetozar Koljević''' ({{lang-sr-cyr|Светозар Кољевић}}; 9 September 1930 – 29 May 2016)<ref>[http://www.rts.rs/page/stories/ci/story/124/drustvo/2335072/preminuo-akademik-svetozar-koljevic.html Преминуо академик Светозар Кољевић] {{sr icon}}</ref> was a Serbian author, historian, translator, and professor, member of the [[Serbian Academy of Sciences and Arts]] and [[Academy of Sciences and Arts of the Republika Srpska]]. He was the elder brother of [[Nikola Koljević]]. His studies focused on South Slavic epic poetry.
