i |first=Tapan |author-mask=2 |date=2007 |title=Bangalanama |publisher=Ananda |location=Kolkata |isbn=978-8177566697}} * {{cite book |last=Raychaudhuri |first=Tapan |author-mask=2 |date=2011 |title=The world in our time: a memoir |publisher=Harper Collins Publishers India |location=Noida |isbn=978-9350291320}}
